<view class="room-page">
  <view class="section-card">
    <view class="section-title">客房送餐识别</view>
    <text class="helper-text">正式环境这里会来自扫码参数。当前先用房间码模拟，例如 `ROOM-801`。</text>
    <input class="room-input" placeholder="请输入房间码" value="{{code}}" bindinput="onInput" />
    <button class="primary-btn room-btn" loading="{{loading}}" bindtap="parseRoom">识别房间</button>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{room}}" class="section-card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title">当前房间</view>
      <button size="mini" bindtap="clearRoom">清除</button>
    </view>
    <view class="room-result">
      <text>房号：{{room.roomNo}}</text>
      <text>楼层：{{room.floorNo}} 层</text>
      <text>场景：{{room.scene}}</text>
    </view>
    <text class="helper-text">房间识别成功后，后续提交订单会自动按客房送餐场景处理。</text>
    <button class="primary-btn room-btn" bindtap="goMenu">去点餐</button>
  </view>
</view>
